<img src="http://c.biz-file.com/c/1802/428793.jpg" alt="Grey Advertising Africa expands strategy team with a new appointment" width="232" height="232">Amy has over five years industry experienced and is a seasoned strategist. “I don’t know how to do anything else, apart from sometimes being an absolute couch potato,” she says. “I am a brand and communication strategist, brand builder and passionate truth seeker. It’s all about creating a balance between analytical thinking, extensive research, gut feel and a little magic,” she continues. When she is not writing a killer strat, she’s watching movies and enjoying junk food on her couch. Her weaknesses are Chicken Licken and cheese.